1
00:00:00,748 --> 00:00:02,810
Previously on The Americans...

2
00:00:02,910 --> 00:00:05,331
The Centre started a
program to develop officers

3
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:07,662
they're calling Second
Generation Illegals.

4
00:00:07,762 --> 00:00:09,386
They want Paige to be next.

5
00:00:09,496 --> 00:00:12,544
I trained as hard as I could every day.

6
00:00:12,654 --> 00:00:14,377
I'm not afraid anymore.

7
00:00:14,477 --> 00:00:16,261
And you're not going to be, either.

8
00:00:16,271 --> 00:00:18,064
So, I met someone.

9
00:00:18,124 --> 00:00:20,355
Hey, this is Philip. Philip, Renee.

10
00:00:20,395 --> 00:00:21,123
Nice to meet you.

11
00:00:21,222 --> 00:00:22,757
She's moving in.

12
00:00:22,856 --> 00:00:24,221
What is it?

13
00:00:24,321 --> 00:00:26,174
Oh, j-just stuff from work.

14
00:00:26,284 --> 00:00:28,206
Oleg Burov is back in Moscow.

15
00:00:28,306 --> 00:00:29,601
We can go with the tape you made of him

16
00:00:29,681 --> 00:00:32,162
admitting their defector
was actually KGB.

17
00:00:32,212 --> 00:00:33,776
You're going to get him killed.

18
00:00:33,876 --> 00:00:36,675
I swore an oath to uphold the
Constitution, Agent Beeman.

19
00:00:36,695 --> 00:00:39,853
Unlike you, I haven't
forgotten what that means.

20
00:00:39,883 --> 00:00:41,298
_

