00:00:44,994 --> 00:00:48,183
When you're walking in the dark,
you don't know the answer,

24
00:00:48,282 --> 00:00:49,578
but you have an instinct...

25
00:00:49,687 --> 00:00:52,278
for how to move forward.

26
00:00:52,377 --> 00:00:53,672
I can't just get this order from them

27
00:00:53,772 --> 00:00:55,765
and do whatever they say.

28
00:00:55,864 --> 00:00:59,391
It's not just me having a hard time.

29
00:00:59,491 --> 00:01:01,244
It's you, too.

30
00:01:01,354 --> 00:01:04,104
We're allowed to have a life.

31
00:01:04,214 --> 00:01:05,708
I can't.

32
00:01:05,808 --> 00:01:07,332
I'm sorry.

33
00:01:08,597 --> 00:01:12,752
Maybe you should stop...
run the travel agency.

34
00:01:12,852 --> 00:01:14,715
You need me, Elizabeth.

35
00:01:14,814 --> 00:01:17,674
I don't want to see you
like this anymore.

36
