278
00:19:11,878 --> 00:19:13,702
And, Rick, your-- your
road trip in the Delta--

279
00:19:13,801 --> 00:19:15,405
- Don't remind me.
- No, no, no.

280
00:19:15,505 --> 00:19:17,428
There you go, because that's
what they need to hear.

281
00:19:17,528 --> 00:19:20,527
